sub_fields.instructions: Please select one or more sub-categories from the list below. To select multiple items, hold down the Ctrl key (on Windows) or the Command key (on Mac) while clicking on the desired sub-categories. You can scroll through the list to find all available options.

sub_fields.label: Local BIA Heading
sub_fields.name: local_bia
sub_fields.instructions: Please select one or more items below. These are internal headings that can be used to classify your business further, and will be available in the business directory.

sub_fields.label: Business Address
sub_fields.name: business_address
sub_fields.instructions: You can enter an address for your business below. Please click on "Add Row" to add a new business address. If you wish to delete an address, please click on the "minus" sign at the end of the address row.
